Give it to 'em yourself.

11:28.150 --> 11:28.990
I would if they was here.

11:29.190 --> 11:30.560
It's your fault they're not.

11:30.760 --> 11:31.780
A nigga just
got in the door, Mo.

11:31.980 --> 11:33.000
Goddamn, man.

11:33.200 --> 11:34.740
This my little cousin, Kitina.

11:34.940 --> 11:36.040
She's in town
from Morris Brown.

11:38.780 --> 11:40.530
You want this?

11:40.730 --> 11:42.440
That's private, Kitina.

11:42.640 --> 11:43.970
And you look a little
too young for it.

11:44.170 --> 11:45.320
It's Tina.

11:45.510 --> 11:47.730
And for your information,
I'm 16.

11:47.930 --> 11:50.230
- Mm.
- [Monique] Smart.

11:50.430 --> 11:53.980
Too damn smart, and always in
everybody's damn business.

11:54.180 --> 11:55.650
If you ever in Hotlanta,
hit me up.

11:55.850 --> 11:56.980
I'll show you around.

11:57.180 --> 11:58.130
What, girl?

11:58.330 --> 12:00.770
[Monique] 16 going on 36.

12:00.970 --> 12:02.250
Girl, bye.

12:02.440 --> 12:05.020
Grown folks got
stuff to discuss.

12:11.550 --> 12:13.170
What the fuck we
gon' do about Lamar?

12:13.370 --> 12:15.110
We tag-team him,
we get this nigga together.

12:15.310 --> 12:17.220
Man, fuck no.
Is you crazy?

12:17.420 --> 12:18.260
I'm not about to have
the mother of my kids

12:18.460 --> 12:20.130
- in no shit like that.
- Motherfucker,

12:20.330 --> 12:22.920
we been past that--I'm still
that nigga Achille's heel.

12:23.120 --> 12:25.290
That nigga Lamar come running
into my every beck and call

12:25.490 --> 12:27.860
like a wounded puppy
or some shit.

12:28.060 --> 12:29.820
Hey Mo, I ain't with this for
real.

12:30.020 --> 12:31.270
[Monique]
Well, you ain't gotta be,

12:31.470 --> 12:32.410
and this is not about you.

12:32.610 --> 12:34.450
This is about me
and my kid's safety.

12:34.650 --> 12:37.050
I'm not jeopardizing that for
you or nobody else no more.

12:39.750 --> 12:41.280
[LaWanda] This is
his favorite necklace

12:41.480 --> 12:43.630
and the belt
he wears the most.

12:43.830 --> 12:44.900
Thank you for coming,
Ms. Joanne.

12:45.100 --> 12:46.460
[Ms. Joanne] Certainly.

12:46.660 --> 12:48.510
Your friend is a man of means.

12:48.710 --> 12:50.100
He likes tea.

12:50.300 --> 12:51.990
The letter or drink?

12:52.190 --> 12:53.950
[LaWanda] Yeah,
well, his name is Terry.

12:54.150 --> 12:56.950
[Ms. Joanne] Oh, yes, Terry.
I was just about to say that.

12:57.150 --> 12:59.260
It also seems that
this man hasn't settled

12:59.460 --> 13:00.990
into his one true path yet.

13:02.380 --> 13:04.570
These all have bad juju.

13:04.770 --> 13:06.440
I'll dispose of them.

13:06.640 --> 13:08.250
[LaWanda] I-I mean, yeah, if-

13:08.450 --> 13:09.730
if that's what
you think is best.

13:09.930 --> 13:11.510
[Ms. Joanne] Certainly.
Hmm.

13:11.710 --> 13:14.140
So, he's a good provider?

13:14.340 --> 13:16.360
For my son, yeah.

13:16.560 --> 13:17.540
Yeah?

13:17.740 --> 13:19.840
<i>Generous?</i>

13:20.040 --> 13:21.520
Joanne,
since you're a psychic,

13:21.720 --> 13:23.410
what we really wanna know

13:23.610 --> 13:25.810
is if this buster's
in it for the long haul.

13:26.010 --> 13:28.830
Yeah, I...I mean,
we gon' be a family or what?

13:29.030 --> 13:32.860
[inhales, exhales]

13:33.060 --> 13:34.550
Give me your hands, ladies.

13:34.750 --> 13:36.110
Give Miss Joanne your hand.

13:39.590 --> 13:41.470
There's something
very pressing

13:41.670 --> 13:44.080
you both need to know.

13:47.080 --> 13:49.210
[bouncer 1] <i>Welcome to the</i>
<i>Rich Man, Poor Man Party.</i>

13:52.650 --> 13:54.360
What up, doe?

13:54.560 --> 13:57.620
[background chatter,
low music plays]

13:57.820 --> 13:59.430
[bouncer 2]
Commission and gifts over there.

13:59.630 --> 14:02.020
All proceeds will be handed out
to the poor later tonight.

14:02.220 --> 14:04.020
- Gentlemen.
- [Terry] What up, doe?

14:04.220 --> 14:05.500
[bouncer 2] Gentlemen.

14:05.700 --> 14:07.150
[Terry] Damn, your boy Rayzin

14:07.350 --> 14:09.150
<i>is dressed to kill for real.</i>

14:09.350 --> 14:10.770
[Meech] <i>Dig honey-dip</i>
<i>over there though?</i>

14:10.960 --> 14:12.700
Yeah, whatever, nigga.
I'm gettin' a drink.

14:12.900 --> 14:14.990
[Meech] A drink?
Man, yo' fruity ass

14:15.190 --> 14:16.420
ain't getting shit
but a Shirley Temple.

14:16.620 --> 14:18.030
[Terry] Hey, shut up, Meech.

14:18.230 --> 14:19.380
Can I get a apple cider,
please?

14:19.580 --> 14:21.280
[Rayzin] What up, doe?

14:21.470 --> 14:23.360
Ain't shit.
Thanks for hearing me out.

14:23.560 --> 14:26.080
Ain't like I had a choice.
You all hot over Sina,

14:26.280 --> 14:27.740
asking me to go behind
my cousin's back.

14:27.940 --> 14:29.440
Now K-9 not even
tripping no more, man.

14:29.640 --> 14:31.220
That nigga done
with the Colombians,

14:31.420 --> 14:32.680
especially with this
new Cali plug he got.

14:32.880 --> 14:34.480
That motherfucker
plays generous...

14:34.680 --> 14:36.530
but K-9's really not.

14:36.730 --> 14:38.360
<i>I remember I once begged</i>
<i>him to break me off.</i>

14:38.560 --> 14:39.490
<i>That motherfucker</i>
<i>threatened me.</i>

14:39.690 --> 14:41.230
Nigga, I'm his blood.

14:41.430 --> 14:42.080
[Meech] <i>You know what</i>
<i>K-9 always told me?</i>

14:42.280 --> 14:43.930
Everybody's got a set price.

14:44.130 --> 14:46.360
I need you to let me know
what your price is.

14:50.450 --> 14:51.980
I want 10% on everything
moving forward.

14:52.180 --> 14:54.050
Nigga, it's done.
Set it up right now.

14:54.250 --> 14:55.240
- Let's get it.
- [Rayzin] <i>Slow your roll homie.</i>

14:55.440 --> 14:56.940
Gotta figure out how
to manage K-9 and Sina.

14:57.140 --> 14:58.810
Not sure Sina'll
wanna hear shit

14:59.010 --> 15:00.210
till that 20 mil's
in his pocket.

15:00.410 --> 15:01.820
- [gunshot]
- [person groans]

15:02.020 --> 15:03.170
[K-9] That's what you
get for ganking me.

15:03.360 --> 15:05.170
- [person] Oh, shit.
- [person] Yo.

15:05.370 --> 15:06.860
Yo, what the fuck?
You just shot Aunt D!

15:07.060 --> 15:08.300
I don't give a fuck!

15:08.500 --> 15:09.950
[woman whimpers]

15:10.150 --> 15:12.390
Sick of her trifling ass
always stealing.

15:12.590 --> 15:14.830
- Quit crying and get up.
- [Dotty] I'm bleeding.

15:15.030 --> 15:16.570
Ma, I ain't
gonna tell you no more.

15:16.770 --> 15:18.960
Get yo' ass up off the floor.

15:19.160 --> 15:21.360
[crying] I can't believe you
just shot me in the head.

15:21.560 --> 15:23.230
[K-9] Man, fuck what
she talking about.

15:23.430 --> 15:25.040
Let's go give this money
to the poor.

15:25.230 --> 15:27.450
[Dotty sobbing]

15:27.650 --> 15:30.340
[heavy music plays]

15:30.540 --> 15:33.100
♪ ♪

15:37.490 --> 15:39.850
[Terry] <i>Yo, fuck</i>
<i>meeting with Sina.</i>

15:40.050 --> 15:41.590
That's a done dilla, Tee.

15:41.790 --> 15:43.120
Yo, that crazy motherfucker

15:43.320 --> 15:44.820
popped his old girl
in the head.

15:45.010 --> 15:46.900
He's the epitome
of a sociopath.

15:47.100 --> 15:50.040
Rayzin's already arranging
our stay in St. Martin.

15:50.240 --> 15:52.130
He's coming with us
to help translate.

15:52.330 --> 15:55.040
Demetrius, are you
fucking listenin' to yourself?

15:55.240 --> 15:56.830
You about to trust
some shady motherfucker

15:57.030 --> 15:59.180
who just turned his back
on his own to help us?

15:59.380 --> 16:01.180
Motherfucker,
we don't know Spanish.

16:01.380 --> 16:03.030
How the hell we
gon' understand each other

16:03.230 --> 16:04.660
- when it's time to translate?
- Nigga, I don't know,

16:04.860 --> 16:07.010
but we not
taking Rayzin with us.

16:07.210 --> 16:09.270
Tee, do you understand
this is bringing us

16:09.470 --> 16:11.780
from buyers to suppliers.

16:11.980 --> 16:14.870
K-9 and Boom is gonna have
to cop from us from now on.

16:15.070 --> 16:16.370
I'm with it.

16:16.570 --> 16:18.090
I'm with all that and some,

16:18.290 --> 16:21.110
but we not taking
K-9's cousin with us.

16:21.310 --> 16:23.510
And hell, push come to shove,
nigga, I'll translate.

16:23.710 --> 16:24.940
With what?

16:25.140 --> 16:26.770
Two high school semesters
of Spanish?

16:26.970 --> 16:28.100
Man, get the fuck outta
here, nigga, talkin' about

16:28.300 --> 16:29.730
- some translating.
- Yeah, well, you--

16:29.930 --> 16:31.510
you heard what the fuck
I said.

16:31.710 --> 16:34.470
[hip-hop playing softly]

16:34.670 --> 16:37.300
Look, Ray is gonna stay put

16:37.500 --> 16:40.370
but your ass better
be on point, nigga.

16:40.570 --> 16:42.390
Yeah, don't...
don't even trip.

16:42.590 --> 16:44.310
I'ma handle the flights
and the weapons.

16:44.510 --> 16:45.920
- We good.
- The weapons?

16:46.120 --> 16:47.490
Nigga, we ain't bringing
no fucking weapons.

16:47.690 --> 16:50.450
Safety first, Meech, always.

16:50.650 --> 16:52.930
I'm not about to meet with no
goddamn cartel with no strap.

16:53.130 --> 16:55.150
We have to demonstrate
trust and respect

16:55.350 --> 16:57.110
in order to solidify this deal.

16:57.300 --> 17:00.460
No straps, flat out.

17:00.660 --> 17:01.710
Fucking L-7.

17:03.450 --> 17:05.580
All right, no straps.

17:08.670 --> 17:11.120
[background chatter,
phone ringing]

17:11.320 --> 17:12.460
Y-you can go.

17:14.590 --> 17:17.390
Hey, uh, two tickets
to St. Martin, please.

17:17.590 --> 17:19.740
Ooh, sounds romantic.

17:19.940 --> 17:21.460
Ah, no, this time
it's for business,

17:21.650 --> 17:22.780
but the next time
might be for pleasure.

17:22.980 --> 17:23.960
Uh, Dwayna.

17:24.160 --> 17:25.790
I should hope so.

17:25.990 --> 17:26.980
You should leave
your card on there too

17:27.180 --> 17:28.660
so I can give you a buzz.

17:28.860 --> 17:30.700
And do you guys have um,
Spanish translations

17:30.900 --> 17:32.100
for your travel guides?

17:32.300 --> 17:34.090
I'll get that
and your tickets right now.

17:36.610 --> 17:39.730
[Markisha] So, they speak
French in St. Martin.

17:39.930 --> 17:41.820
Dutch on the other side,
and English in both.

17:42.020 --> 17:43.760
So why Spanish?

17:43.960 --> 17:44.980
'Cause it's a
tourist place, you know?

17:45.180 --> 17:46.590
You never know where the
honeys are gonna be from.

17:46.790 --> 17:48.130
[Dwayna]
<i>I'm sorry, Mr. Flenory.</i>

17:48.330 --> 17:50.420
Our guides don't have
that kind of glossary.

17:50.620 --> 17:54.460
Here's a place you can
take a crash course tonight.

17:56.330 --> 17:58.210
[Terry]
<i>Yeah, I'll think about it.</i>

17:58.410 --> 17:59.820
Oh, and then we could--
we could throw these out,

18:00.020 --> 18:01.450
'cause I'm no longer
in the car-ride business.

18:01.650 --> 18:05.390
Thank you so much, Dwayna?
Dwayna.

18:05.590 --> 18:06.690
<i>Excuse me, guy.</i>

18:08.730 --> 18:10.770
[Lamar] Come on Blackie, sit.

18:10.960 --> 18:13.960
Sit, Blackie.

18:14.160 --> 18:16.620
[Monique] <i>Wow, you got</i>
<i>him trained pretty well.</i>

18:16.820 --> 18:18.620
Yeah, a little TLC
is all it take.

18:18.820 --> 18:19.960
[Monique] Have a seat.

18:23.440 --> 18:26.480
Look, I've been thinking about
what you said Meech did to you,

18:26.680 --> 18:28.570
and that shit really fucked up.

18:28.770 --> 18:29.890
There's no
need to apologize, Mo.

18:30.090 --> 18:31.900
[Monique] I do.

18:32.090 --> 18:33.160
I've been thinking about
building our family back,

18:33.360 --> 18:36.380
but I can't because I lied.

18:36.580 --> 18:39.470
I told you that you
weren't Zoe's father,

18:39.670 --> 18:41.300
but you really are.

18:41.500 --> 18:43.070
[small laugh] What?

18:45.290 --> 18:47.780
Well, I knew...
I knew she was mine.

18:47.980 --> 18:49.700
Look, after
hearing your story,

18:49.900 --> 18:51.940
I don't wanna keep
Zoe away from you,

18:52.140 --> 18:54.090
but a lot has
happened between us.

18:54.290 --> 18:55.790
I know. I know.

18:55.990 --> 18:58.340
And it's-it's gon' take time
to build the trust back.

18:58.530 --> 19:00.580
But I-I'm willing to do it

19:00.780 --> 19:01.790
one step at a time.

19:01.990 --> 19:03.640
<i>You see that, Blackie?</i>

19:03.840 --> 19:05.100
<i>- We got you back on your feet.</i>
- [Blackie whines]

19:05.300 --> 19:06.670
<i>Now your old man is too.</i>

19:06.870 --> 19:08.060
Come on.

19:08.260 --> 19:10.110
Go give Mama some sugar.

19:10.310 --> 19:11.980
- [Blackie whines]
- Look like he sick

19:12.180 --> 19:13.280
or need some water
or somethin'.

19:13.480 --> 19:15.030
I don't know.

19:15.220 --> 19:16.810
Look, I need to get him
back to the house,

19:17.010 --> 19:19.120
so I'ma hit you up later on.

19:19.320 --> 19:20.590
All right. Cool.

19:23.720 --> 19:25.750
I-I can't get a hug goodbye?

19:25.950 --> 19:28.820
Nah. We said we was
gonna move slow

19:29.020 --> 19:30.820
and build that trust back,
right?

19:31.020 --> 19:33.390
- Right.
- Right.

19:33.590 --> 19:35.170
I mean, it was worth a try.

19:38.650 --> 19:40.620
All right.
Come on, Blackie.

19:40.820 --> 19:42.130
Let's bounce.

19:49.920 --> 19:52.450
Whoo. Shit.

19:52.650 --> 19:55.260
[moody music plays]

19:55.460 --> 19:58.190
♪ ♪

20:04.670 --> 20:05.990
[Terry] <i>That's bullshit.</i>

20:06.190 --> 20:07.300
You go to some
goddamn palm reader

20:07.490 --> 20:09.300
and you come back
swearing you knocked up.

20:09.500 --> 20:10.520
I'm getting you
another test, LaWanda.

20:10.720 --> 20:11.780
[LaWanda] Oh my gosh, Terry.

20:11.980 --> 20:13.300
I'd already taken
three tests by then.

20:13.500 --> 20:15.000
She just confirmed it,

20:15.200 --> 20:16.630
saying there'd be a new
addition to the family

20:16.830 --> 20:18.440
<i>and not everybody</i>
<i>would be happy.</i>

20:18.640 --> 20:19.870
I don't give a damn
what she confirmed.

20:20.070 --> 20:21.530
You're gonna take another test,

20:21.730 --> 20:23.180
and you better go back
to that little Santeria witch

20:23.380 --> 20:24.700
and get the rest
of my shit back.

20:24.900 --> 20:26.640
<i>You already know</i>
<i>false prophets</i>

20:26.840 --> 20:28.290
<i>- are against my religion.</i>
- [LaWanda] <i>You know what?</i>

20:28.490 --> 20:29.580
You ain't got no religion.
Only time you talk about God

20:29.780 --> 20:31.190
is when it's convenient
for you,

20:31.390 --> 20:33.540
- and I'm sick of it, actually--
- [Désirée] Terry. Now...

20:33.740 --> 20:35.280
I do my best to stay out of

20:35.480 --> 20:37.040
your and LaWanda's
relationship,

20:37.240 --> 20:40.390
but I do wanna remind you
that babies are blessings.

20:40.590 --> 20:42.770
<i>You just gonna turn your back</i>
<i>on what the Lord's given you?</i>

20:42.960 --> 20:44.640
Yeah, you know what?
I'm-I'm out.

20:44.840 --> 20:46.640
- [Désirée] Terry!
- I'm out. Leave me alone.

20:46.840 --> 20:47.940
[door slams]

20:53.030 --> 20:54.560
[Terry] <i>Meech and I have</i>
<i>a big business opportunity</i>

20:54.760 --> 20:55.990
<i>with the Colombians,</i>
<i>but, um...</i>

20:58.120 --> 21:00.910
You know, after that note
that you wrote me, I...

21:01.110 --> 21:04.220
I didn't think you ever
wanted to talk to me again.

21:04.420 --> 21:06.400
Sorry for how I acted.

21:06.600 --> 21:08.900
You're not a boy.

21:09.100 --> 21:12.100
[Spanish guitar plays
nearby]

21:12.300 --> 21:13.930
[exhales] So, look,

21:14.130 --> 21:16.450
if all goes well
with the Colombians,

21:16.650 --> 21:19.540
I'll be able to care
for you and the ninos.

21:19.740 --> 21:21.020
[Markisha giggles]

21:21.220 --> 21:24.980
And no, not in no hotel.

21:25.180 --> 21:27.700
<i>Una casa.</i>
<i>Nuestra casa.</i>

21:27.900 --> 21:30.020
All right, well, then
bring it on home, Tee.

21:31.200 --> 21:32.860
Don't forget...

21:33.060 --> 21:34.320
you're the closer.

21:34.520 --> 21:36.380
[wheels rattling]

21:36.580 --> 21:37.990
A rose
for the beautiful lady.

21:38.190 --> 21:41.520
Uh, yeah, you know what?
Let me get all of 'em.

21:41.720 --> 21:43.470
- Keep the change.
- [Markisha] Thank you.

21:45.340 --> 21:46.520
Thank you.

21:49.740 --> 21:52.440
[speaking Spanish]

21:52.640 --> 21:55.770
Uh, <i>no entiendo,</i>but...
<i>me gusta.</i>

21:55.970 --> 21:56.960
[laughs]

21:59.660 --> 22:01.280
Look,
forgive my two left feet,

22:01.480 --> 22:03.720
but somehow we still in sync.

22:03.920 --> 22:05.980
[Markisha] Thank you
for my flowers.

22:06.180 --> 22:08.420
[Terry] You're the greatest
gift a guy could ask for.

22:08.620 --> 22:10.320
If you're mine, that is.

22:12.800 --> 22:14.630
And since we starting
things off right...

22:16.240 --> 22:18.510
...I wanna be honest with you.

22:18.710 --> 22:20.860
LaWanda's pregnant again.

22:21.060 --> 22:23.260
She says it's mine, but...

22:23.460 --> 22:26.350
it must have been
before you and I got serious.

22:26.550 --> 22:30.020
[guitar continues
in background]

22:30.220 --> 22:32.790
♪ ♪

22:32.990 --> 22:34.350
Wow, Terry.

22:37.440 --> 22:39.930
Come on, Markisha.
I'm not in love with her.

22:40.130 --> 22:41.530
I love you.

22:47.050 --> 22:49.200
[Lucille] <i>I just thought it</i>
<i>was really important</i>

22:49.400 --> 22:52.110
for all us women to get
together and just talk.

22:52.310 --> 22:54.010
[LaWanda] Yes, with no men.

22:54.200 --> 22:55.770
- [Nicole] Amen.
- [light giggling]

22:55.970 --> 22:57.160
[Désirée] Well,
thanks for having us.

22:57.360 --> 22:59.210
I mean, Wanda loves it here.

22:59.410 --> 23:00.690
<i>She's here more than home.</i>

23:00.890 --> 23:02.410
Well, that's 'cause of TJ.

23:02.600 --> 23:04.600
[Lucille] Honey, we all
know why you come over,

23:04.800 --> 23:08.130
and I just want you to know
that we support you 100%.

23:08.330 --> 23:09.960
Yeah. It ain't our fault
Tee's such a idiot.

23:10.160 --> 23:12.440
- [light laughter]
- [Désirée] <i>Honestly,</i>

23:12.640 --> 23:15.480
you should have heard
the way he spoke to her.

23:15.680 --> 23:18.570
Terry can be blunt,
but he will always,

23:18.770 --> 23:21.450
always take care of
his obligations.

23:21.650 --> 23:23.670
Oh...[scoffs]
My daughter and grandson

23:23.860 --> 23:25.560
are not obligations.

23:25.760 --> 23:28.000
I mean, really, can't you
find a way to control him?

23:28.190 --> 23:30.670
[Lucille]
Now, Désirée, Wanda and I

23:30.870 --> 23:32.940
have tried to force Terry

